<br>
But all that has changed, Apollo has decided to return to Olympus, and with him the light and happiness that he had taken with him when he left.<br>
<br>
::his golden horse drawn chariot rips across the sky surrounded by flocks of swans and crows.A smile rides itself across his angelic face as he is elated to return home to his family and friends:: <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugoddessartemis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goddess Artemis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Goddess</span><br>  Posts: 20<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/1/01 7:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> * upon his return *</span><hr size=1> * Artemis sits alone in her chambers, layed upon her bed of silks, her white gown layed out around her in a soft spill, she is laying on her stomach popping some ambosia in her mouth and reading a scroll from an Amazon that wishes she was with child, asking Artemis to bless her, her auburn locks fall past her shoulders in waves like the ocean. In a sudden movement, she gets out of bed, dropping the book, she gasps and runs out to the balcony overlooking the lands far below, she senses, more then sees her brother, she knows that he is on his way back home, where he belongs. She smiles, giddy with excitment, wanting to hear of all the adventures he has been on since he left. Thinking, she turns and runs to the throne room to ready his throne...finally her beloved twin is retuning home * <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uthegreatapollo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Great Apollo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 3<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/1/01 7:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?to