 he walked around the room and then settle into his throne.  Despite the frustration in their relationship..she was always taken aback by his powerful presence.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uzeuskingofthegods.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zeus King of the Gods</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 1<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/3/01 11:51 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic&index=16>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: and things settle</span><hr size=1> Zeus watched the activity.  He nodded and smiled politely to those acknowledging him.  He winked at Hera noting her intent gaze on him.  He stood proclaiming a toast.  A mugful of ambrosia appeared in the hands of all those present.  &quot;To your shining son of Olympus.  May our days be all the more glorious with his return.&quot;  He held his glass high and then put it to his lips and drank the cool nectar of the gods.  <br>
<br>
He smirked then walked to the reflecting pool to gaze down at the mortals. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/ugoddessartemis.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Goddess Artemis</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Goddess</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/4/01 1:56 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm23.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=33.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=img WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: and things settle</span><hr size=1> * Artemis runs into the throne room, her barefeet slapping against the hard floor, she stops as she runs headon into her twin and embraces him in a hug smiling*<br>
